<topic id="whr-html5-pages">
    <title>HTML5 Responsive Pages</title>
    <body>
    <p>You can select from several different styles of layouts (for example, by default, you can
      select either a <i>tiles</i> or <i>tree</i> style of layout). Furthermore, each of these
      layouts include a collection of skins that you can choose from, or you can customize your
      own.</p>
    <p>
      <fig id="fig_y5z_p2f_dr">
        <title>WebHelp Responsive Output on a Normal Screen</title>
        <image href="../img/WebHelpResponsiveFlower.png" id="image_nvz_p2f_dr"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <title>WebHelp Responsive Output on a Narrow Screen </title>
        <image href="../img/WebHelpResponsiveMobileFlower.png"/>
